data.description: Welcome to your new home 1129 Byberry Road ! This delightful single rancher is a perfect blend of comfort and style, offering a cozy retreat in a convenient location. Upon entering you are greeted with an abundance of natural lighting creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout the home. This home features 3 nice size bedrooms, a fully updated bathroom and 1/2 bath in your Master bedroom. Laundry area conveniently located by the hallway next to the kitchen.  Off the kitchen you will find a   bonus/family room  space for all your family gatherings.  Spacious backyard with above pool and patio awaits your summer BBQs.   This home has been meticulously cared for, ensuring a move-in-ready experience for the lucky new homeowners. This charming rancher is not just a house; it's a place to call your new home. Don't miss the opportunity to make cherished memories in this wonderful property.
